column100: Vi søger en kollega til dagholds-produktionen i Hasle   På fabrikken i Hasle producerer Espersen Filet-O-Fish til McDonald’s i hele Europa.   Produktionen er automatiseret og opgaverne vil primært være udpakning af blokke og overvågning af maskine, som fodres med de frosne fiskeblokke der efter viderebehandling til slut pakkes i æsker og transporteret til frostlageret.   Truckkørekort vil være en fordel, men ikke noget krav.   Se mere om produktionen her i Youtube videoen:  https://youtu.be/6mRa1G8L1no   Løn iht. Lokalaftale og Industriens Overenskomst.   Ring gerne til undertegnede og hør mere om jobbet.   Preben Finne   Production Supervisor   Tlf. 21 17 41 01   PS. For at kunne varetage jobbet forventer vi, at du bor eller bosætter dig på Bornholm.     We are looking for a colleague for the day shift production in Hasle   At the Hasle factory, Espersen produces Filet-O-Fish for McDonald's throughout Europe.   The production is automated and the tasks will primarily be unpacking of blocks and monitoring of the machine, which is fed with the frozen fish blocks which after further processing are finally packed in boxes and transported to the frost storage.   Truck driving license will be an advantage but not a requirement.   See more about the production here in the Youtube video:  https://youtu.be/6mRa1G8L1no     Salary according to Local Agreement and Industrial Agreement.   Feel free to call the undersigned and hear more about the job.   Preben Finne   Production Supervisor   Phone: 21 17 41 01   PS. In order to perform the job, we expect you to live or settle on Bornholm.
